title: Windows 8 Permanent Volume License Activator
description:
No watermarks
No KMS
Bo requirement to rearm
To install right mouse click on "Install.cmd" and select "Run as  administrator" and your done.  

You can verify all licensing just open a command prompt and type the following to check; 
1. Current licensing status
2. Activation information
3. Expiration date 
 
1.	slmgr -dlv
2.	slmgr -dli
3.	slmgr -xpr

If Retail Disc is used add ei.cfg to /sources directory to skip entering a key
